# 🏥 Hospital Management System (Tkinter + MySQL)

A desktop-based **Hospital Management System** built with **Python Tkinter** and **MySQL**.  
This system allows storing, updating, deleting, and retrieving patient & prescription records efficiently.

---

## 🚀 Features
- Add new patient & prescription records  
- Update existing records  
- Delete records using Reference Number  
- Reset/Clear all input fields  
- Search & view patient details in a tabular format  
- Auto-fetch records into the Tkinter TreeView table  
- MySQL database integration for secure storage  

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- **Python (Tkinter)** – GUI frontend  
- **MySQL (pymysql)** – Database management  
- **ttk (TreeView)** – For displaying patient records in a table  

---

## 📂 Project Structure
hospital_management/
│-- hospital.py # Main Python Tkinter application
│-- requirements.txt # Dependencies
│-- README.md # Documentation
